---
import { EXPERIENCE } from '../constants';
import LinkButton from './LinkButton.astro';
---

<div class='flex flex-col gap-4 sm:gap-8'>
	<h2 class='font-bold text-6xl sm:text-8xl'>{EXPERIENCE}</h2>
	<div class='flex flex-col gap-8'>
		<div class='flex flex-col gap-4'>
			<div class='flex flex-col gap-2'>
				<h3 class='font-bold text-2xl'>
					Frontend developer @
					<a class='underline' target='_blank' href='https://www.reservio.com'>
						Reservio
					</a>
				</h3>
				<h4 class='italic'>November 2021 - Present</h4>
				<p class='flex flex-row items-start'>
					<img src='./public/chevron-right.svg' width={24} />
					Delivered new features for a reservations system in a self-organizing manner
					from refinement with the product manager to deploying to production.
				</p>
				<p>
					Skills: React, Next.js, TypeScript, Apollo, GraphQL, REST, React Hook
					Form, CSS-in-JS
				</p>
			</div>
			<LinkButton icon='play-fill' href='https://second-job.martinjordan.dev'>
				Skills showcase
			</LinkButton>
		</div>

		<div class='flex flex-col gap-2'>
			<h3 class='font-bold text-2xl'>
				Scrum master @
				<a class='underline' target='_blank' href='https://www.24i.com'>24i</a>
			</h3>
			<h4 class='italic'>February 2021 - October 2021</h4>
			<ul class='flex flex-col gap-1'>
				<li class='flex flex-row items-start'>
					<img src='./public/chevron-right.svg' width={24} />
					Facilitated remote Scrum ceremonies for up to 3 international teams.
				</li>
				<li class='flex flex-row items-start'>
					<img src='./public/chevron-right.svg' width={24} />
					<span>
						Defined team member's roles and responsibilities in the engineering
						department of 60 people.
					</span>
				</li>
				<li class='flex flex-row items-start'>
					<img src='./public/chevron-right.svg' width={24} />
					Reduced management complexity across 9 engineering teams by unifying ways
					of working.
				</li>
			</ul>
			<p>Skills: Communication, Meeting organization, Planning</p>
		</div>

		<div class='flex flex-col gap-4'>
			<div class='flex flex-col gap-2'>
				<h3 class='font-bold text-2xl'>
					Javascript developer @
					<a class='underline' target='_blank' href='https://www.24i.com'>24i</a
					>
				</h3>
				<h4 class='italic'>November 2018 - February 2021</h4>
				<ul>
					<li class='flex flex-row items-start'>
						<img src='./public/chevron-right.svg' width={24} />
						Implemented several functionalities for Smart TV devices (Samsung, LG).
					</li>
				</ul>
				<p>Skills: React, TypeScript, Sass</p>
			</div>
			<LinkButton icon='play-fill' href='https://first-job.martinjordan.dev'>
				Skills showcase
			</LinkButton>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
